Class GbifUser

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.common.AbstractGbifUser
org.gbif.api.model.common.GbifUser
public class GbifUser extends AbstractGbifUser
A GBIF user account registered in the user Identity database (previously Drupal). This class is the replacement of User.
